The wolf had been planning to eat the third pig, but he was like, "this is getting ridiculous."  He knew there were one hundred of the, all on the same street.  He looked up and down the road, in the distance the straw and wood houses were flattened, an the brick house was still standing.  From there on he could see his failure, one house after another.  In the other direction were just a few more houses, each looked different from the next, he was no expert, but he could tell they were made of different materials.  Based on the last ninety experiences he suspected the future was not promising, was that last one diamond!  It had taken him to this point, but he started to realize he needed a change in approach.  he wolf was not a stupid wolf, he was a wolf of many talents.

Then off in the distance he saw a girl heading into the forest, easy to spot with that red hooded cloak.  Now, where was that granny costume he used to entertain his friends?  He had a plan.
